645
00:35:39,000 --> 00:35:42,060
[Kim Han Gyeol: Oh, they're all smiling!]

646
00:35:42,290 --> 00:35:44,700
[Kim Han Gyeol: I want to feed you, but I can't.]

647
00:35:44,700 --> 00:35:48,190
[Kim Han Gyeol: The sign says we can't feed you.]

648
00:35:48,190 --> 00:35:50,560
[(Turns away)]
[Lee Hyun Jun: They understood you.]

649
00:35:50,560 --> 00:35:51,280
OK.

650
00:35:51,360 --> 00:35:54,400
[Lee Hyeok Jin: OK. Take care.]
[Kim Han Gyeol: I'm sorry.]

651
00:35:56,430 --> 00:35:57,470
They go "Baa."

652
00:35:58,760 --> 00:36:02,560
[Lee Hyun Jun: The donkey is glaring at us!]
[Kim Han Gyeol: Oh, it's scary.]

653
00:36:03,560 --> 00:36:07,080
[Lee Hyeok Jin: They all crowd around the food.]
[Kim Han Gyeol: Yeah.]

654
00:36:07,240 --> 00:36:07,690
[Lee Hyun Jun: So cute.]

655
00:36:07,690 --> 00:36:10,950
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Is it that delicious?]
[Kim Han Gyeol: I know, right?]

656
00:36:10,950 --> 00:36:13,180
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Want to try it?]

657
00:36:13,180 --> 00:36:15,420
[Kim Han Gyeol:
You try it first and then we'll join you.]

658
00:36:15,870 --> 00:36:19,310
[Kim Han Gyeol: Look at its aura.]
[Lee Hyeok Jin: It may really be the leader.]

659
00:36:19,310 --> 00:36:21,750
[Kim Han Gyeol: I think that's the Muscovy duck.]

660
00:36:23,890 --> 00:36:25,790
[Lee Hyun Jun: I want to eat duck.]

661
00:36:25,790 --> 00:36:28,180
[Lee Hyeok Jin: When you're looking at ducks?]
[Kim Han Gyeol: Are you serious?]

662
00:36:28,180 --> 00:36:31,200
[Lee Hyeok Jin:
Seriously... But sounds delicious.]

663
00:36:31,200 --> 00:36:33,800
[Kim Han Gyeol: I'll need mustard.]

664
00:36:34,100 --> 00:36:37,370
[Kim Han Gyeol:
I saw a new side of Hyun Jun today.]

665
00:36:37,680 --> 00:36:41,780
[Kim Han Gyeol: I thought he was
just cold and stoic, but he loves animals.]

666
00:36:41,780 --> 00:36:45,030
[Kim Han Gyeol: He is surprisingly pure.]

667
00:36:45,300 --> 00:36:47,710
[Kim Han Gyeol:
I find him much more approachable.]

668
00:36:48,310 --> 00:36:50,740
[Lee Hyeok Jin: I chose the two of them,]

669
00:36:51,020 --> 00:36:54,130
[Lee Hyeok Jin:
but I think they had more fun than me.]

670
00:36:54,640 --> 00:36:57,380
[Lee Hyeok Jin: It wasn't a satisfying date.]

671
00:36:57,610 --> 00:37:01,530
[Lee Hyeok Jin: I regret the choices I made.]

672
00:37:01,790 --> 00:37:05,910
["It was a very forgettable date."]

673
00:37:06,570 --> 00:37:11,940
[Hyeok Jin's date leaves him
with regret and disappointment]

674
00:37:12,140 --> 00:37:13,410
[Kim Sun Wook: What's wrong?]

675
00:37:13,410 --> 00:37:15,710
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Well...]
[Kim Sun Wook: Yeah?]

676
00:37:15,710 --> 00:37:17,420
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Just now...]

677
00:37:17,420 --> 00:37:19,220
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Was it at breakfast?]

678
00:37:19,220 --> 00:37:21,700
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I talked to Hyeok Jin over there]

679
00:37:21,700 --> 00:37:23,290
[Eum Hyeok Jin: about the phone calls.]

680
00:37:23,290 --> 00:37:26,990
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Hyeok Jin said
he called (Han Gyeol). I said I called him too.]

681
00:37:26,990 --> 00:37:29,930
[Eum Hyeok Jin: But when playing board games,]

682
00:37:29,930 --> 00:37:33,770
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I asked Han Gyeol out
for a walk together sometime.]

683
00:37:33,770 --> 00:37:36,070
[Eum Hyeok Jin: He said, "OK."]

684
00:37:36,070 --> 00:37:40,570
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Hyeok Jin knows
that I'm interested in (Han Gyeol).]

685
00:37:40,570 --> 00:37:44,530
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
When he was choosing his dates,]

686
00:37:44,530 --> 00:37:47,400
[Eum Hyeok Jin: after choosing Han Gyeol,
he seemed conscious about my reaction.]

687
00:37:47,400 --> 00:37:49,810
[Kim Sun Wook: Who?]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: (Lee) Hyeok Jin.]

688
00:37:49,810 --> 00:37:53,060
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I was thinking, "Don't pick him."]

689
00:37:53,060 --> 00:37:56,330
[Eum Hyeok Jin: If he didn't pick him, I could've]

690
00:37:56,330 --> 00:37:58,330
[Eum Hyeok Jin: gone on a walk with him.]

691
00:37:59,330 --> 00:38:01,200
[Eum Hyeok Jin: That's what I thought.]

692
00:38:01,200 --> 00:38:05,300
[Eum Hyeok Jin: But he still chose him.]
[Kim Sun Wook: Yeah.]

693
00:38:05,300 --> 00:38:07,810
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Nothing's going my way.]

694
00:38:07,810 --> 00:38:09,500
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I have no chance to...]

695
00:38:09,500 --> 00:38:10,640
[Eum Hyeok Jin: to impress him]

696
00:38:10,640 --> 00:38:13,120
[Eum Hyeok Jin: and make an impression.]

697
00:38:13,120 --> 00:38:17,870
[Eum Hyeok Jin: So I'm... getting anxious.]

698
00:38:17,870 --> 00:38:19,490
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I don't know what to do now.]

699
00:38:19,490 --> 00:38:22,130
[Kim Sun Wook: It's OK. You'll get your chance.]

700
00:38:22,130 --> 00:38:26,590
[Kim Sun Wook: There will always be chances.]

701
00:38:26,590 --> 00:38:28,230
[Kim Sun Wook:
What should we do in this huge house?]

702
00:38:28,230 --> 00:38:29,880
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Should we lie down?]

703
00:38:29,880 --> 00:38:31,600
[Kim Sun Wook: Shall we?]

704
00:38:33,000 --> 00:38:36,100
[Eum Hyeok Jin: So now I'm so...]

705
00:38:36,100 --> 00:38:38,770
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I'm so stressed.]

706
00:38:38,770 --> 00:38:42,150
[Kim Sun Wook: You know what's funny?
I asked him out on a date today,]

707
00:38:42,150 --> 00:38:45,250
[Kim Sun Wook:
but now he's on a date, and I'm not.]

708
00:38:45,880 --> 00:38:47,380
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Su Min?]
[Kim Sun Wook: Huh?]

709
00:38:47,380 --> 00:38:49,730
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Su Min?]
[Kim Sun Wook: No.]

710
00:38:49,730 --> 00:38:52,780
[Kim Sun Wook: Hyun Jun.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Oh, I see.]

711
00:38:52,780 --> 00:38:54,430
[Eum Hyeok Jin: You know what else's funny?]

712
00:38:54,430 --> 00:38:56,330
[Eum Hyeok Jin: (Lee Hyeok Jin) told me]
[Kim Sun Wook: What?]

713
00:38:56,330 --> 00:38:59,420
[Eum Hyeok Jin: that he asked Hyun Jun out today.]

714
00:38:59,420 --> 00:39:01,150
[Kim Sun Wook: He did?]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Yeah.]

715
00:39:01,150 --> 00:39:01,760
[Kim Sun Wook: Today?]

716
00:39:01,760 --> 00:39:03,030
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Yeah, he asked him out.]

717
00:39:03,030 --> 00:39:05,460
[Kim Sun Wook: He asked him out today?]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Yeah.]

718
00:39:05,460 --> 00:39:07,620
[Kim Sun Wook: Seriously?]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Yeah.]

719
00:39:09,010 --> 00:39:11,390
[Kim Sun Wook: Ah... Wow...]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: It's really messy now.]

720
00:39:11,390 --> 00:39:13,920
[Kim Sun Wook: I asked him out too!]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I know.]

721
00:39:13,920 --> 00:39:15,590
[Eum Hyeok Jin: But it can't be helped.]

722
00:39:15,590 --> 00:39:17,180
[Eum Hyeok Jin: We are in the same boat.]

723
00:39:17,180 --> 00:39:18,830
[Kim Sun Wook: Wow, now I'm...]

724
00:39:18,830 --> 00:39:23,810
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I also asked Han Gyeol on a date.]
[Kim Sun Wook: And he's on a date now.]

725
00:39:23,810 --> 00:39:26,210
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
Yeah, because he was chosen as a date.]

726
00:39:26,210 --> 00:39:30,760
[Kim Sun Wook: Lee Hyeok Jin...]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: He took our crushes away.]

727
00:39:30,760 --> 00:39:32,450
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Right now,]

728
00:39:32,450 --> 00:39:34,170
[Eum Hyeok Jin: we can't see him as an ally]

729
00:39:34,170 --> 00:39:37,980
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
and be too open about our feelings.]

730
00:39:38,340 --> 00:39:40,940
[Eum Hyeok Jin: To be precise, he is our rival.]

731
00:39:40,940 --> 00:39:43,140
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
Isn't he? With how things are going.]

732
00:39:46,520 --> 00:39:49,140
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Didn't expect this, right?]

733
00:39:49,140 --> 00:39:51,000
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Right? Don't you agree?]

734
00:39:52,950 --> 00:39:55,450
[Kim Sun Wook: Gosh, what is this?]

735
00:39:55,450 --> 00:39:57,020
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I don't know!]

736
00:39:58,540 --> 00:39:59,480
[Cho Yun Jae: What are you doing?]

737
00:39:59,480 --> 00:40:00,910
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I was about to go up.]

738
00:40:00,910 --> 00:40:02,630
[Eum Hyeok Jin: You were alone, right?]
[Cho Yun Jae: Yeah.]

739
00:40:02,630 --> 00:40:04,090
[Kim Sun Wook: Come on the bed.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Yeah, sit here.]

740
00:40:04,090 --> 00:40:08,000
[Cho Yun Jae: I'm comfortable here, on the floor.]

741
00:40:08,000 --> 00:40:10,340
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Since you've hit rock bottom.]

742
00:40:13,010 --> 00:40:14,220
[Cho Yun Jae: So mean.]

743
00:40:14,220 --> 00:40:18,840
[Eum Hyeok Jin: So... how are things?]

744
00:40:18,840 --> 00:40:20,990
[Eum Hyeok Jin: How you...]
[Cho Yun Jae: How I feel?]

745
00:40:20,990 --> 00:40:24,860
[Cho Yun Jae: Tell me about you first.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Me?]

746
00:40:27,560 --> 00:40:28,720
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I don't know.]

747
00:40:30,460 --> 00:40:33,070
[Kim Sun Wook: I'm curious too.]
[Cho Yun Jae: I'm really curious.]

748
00:40:33,070 --> 00:40:36,800
[Cho Yun Jae: Is it the guy you called yesterday?]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Of course.]

749
00:40:37,220 --> 00:40:38,910
[Cho Yun Jae: I see...]

750
00:40:38,910 --> 00:40:40,550
[Eum Hyeok Jin: But there was one thing.]

751
00:40:40,550 --> 00:40:43,740
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
The guy I called couldn't guess who I was.]

752
00:40:43,740 --> 00:40:45,510
[Kim Sun Wook: But now he knows.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Yeah.]

753
00:40:45,510 --> 00:40:48,290
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
He asked me while being clueless.]

754
00:40:48,290 --> 00:40:49,680
[Cho Yun Jae: I know who it is!]

755
00:40:49,680 --> 00:40:52,040
[Cho Yun Jae: I know it now. Didn't mean to.]

756
00:40:52,040 --> 00:40:57,480
[Eum Hyeok Jin: But since he got 4 calls...]

757
00:40:57,480 --> 00:40:58,420
[Eum Hyeok Jin: There's one more...]

758
00:40:58,420 --> 00:41:01,760
[Kim Sun Wook: Hyeong Jun.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Really?]

759
00:41:01,760 --> 00:41:03,580
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I didn't know that.]

760
00:41:03,580 --> 00:41:06,130
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Hyeong Jun called Han Gyeol?]

761
00:41:06,130 --> 00:41:08,590
[Kim Sun Wook:
Maybe I'm wrong, but that's what I thought.]

762
00:41:08,590 --> 00:41:11,070
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I didn't know about Hyeong Jun.]

763
00:41:11,070 --> 00:41:12,370
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I only knew Taichi and...]

764
00:41:12,370 --> 00:41:14,930
[Kim Sun Wook: Did you get a text yesterday?]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Did you get a call?]

765
00:41:15,900 --> 00:41:16,730
[Kim Sun Wook: Then...]

766
00:41:16,730 --> 00:41:18,760
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Hyun Jun must've called him.]

767
00:41:21,890 --> 00:41:23,940
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I wonder what Taichi felt]

768
00:41:23,940 --> 00:41:27,780
[Eum Hyeok Jin: watching his roommate
get 3 calls on top of his call.]

769
00:41:27,780 --> 00:41:29,530
[Kim Sun Wook: He must've liked it.]

770
00:41:29,530 --> 00:41:32,350
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Why? Oh, because he won.]
[Kim Sun Wook: Because Han Gyeol chose him.]

771
00:41:32,350 --> 00:41:33,670
[Eum Hyeok Jin: But...]

772
00:41:33,670 --> 00:41:36,320
[Eum Hyeok Jin: From what I know of Taichi,
he might have guessed the callers with him.]

773
00:41:36,320 --> 00:41:37,660
[Kim Sun Wook: He must've guessed.]

774
00:41:37,660 --> 00:41:40,070
[Kim Sun Wook: It's only human to be curious.]

775
00:41:40,070 --> 00:41:41,860
[Cho Yun Jae: Yeah.]

776
00:41:41,860 --> 00:41:43,420
[Kim Sun Wook: Same for everyone.]

777
00:41:43,420 --> 00:41:44,880
[Eum Hyeok Jin: The more I think about it,]

778
00:41:44,880 --> 00:41:46,770
[Eum Hyeok Jin: the more I have bad thoughts.]

779
00:41:46,770 --> 00:41:48,190
[Kim Sun Wook: It's normal to have bad thoughts.]

780
00:41:48,190 --> 00:41:52,200
[Kim Sun Wook: As long as
you don't put those thoughts into action.]

781
00:41:52,200 --> 00:41:55,880
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
Actually, I might take action too.]

782
00:41:55,880 --> 00:41:58,440
[Kim Sun Wook:
What action? What are you up to?]

783
00:41:58,440 --> 00:42:02,780
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
If he's determined, I can make it happen.]

784
00:42:02,780 --> 00:42:05,260
[Kim Sun Wook: I'm curious.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Anyway, for me,]

785
00:42:05,260 --> 00:42:08,160
[Eum Hyeok Jin: if he's so determined,]

786
00:42:08,160 --> 00:42:11,950
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
I'll restrain myself. Otherwise...]

787
00:42:11,950 --> 00:42:15,570
[Kim Sun Wook: But here's what I think.
It's only the second day.]

788
00:42:15,570 --> 00:42:17,400
[Eum Hyeok Jin: It's just my fantasy.]

789
00:42:17,400 --> 00:42:20,360
[Kim Sun Wook:
There's always room to make a move.]

790
00:42:20,360 --> 00:42:23,300
[Kim Sun Wook:
Everyone has his own secret weapon.]

791
00:42:23,300 --> 00:42:24,850
[Kim Sun Wook: So,]

792
00:42:24,850 --> 00:42:27,200
[Kim Sun Wook: let's use it when we can.]

793
00:42:27,200 --> 00:42:28,240
[Eum Hyeok Jin: But let's say]

794
00:42:28,240 --> 00:42:29,940
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I'm better at 1-on-1 dates.]

795
00:42:29,940 --> 00:42:32,180
[Eum Hyeok Jin: But I don't get a chance to...]

796
00:42:32,180 --> 00:42:34,190
[Kim Sun Wook: Can't be alone with him.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Yeah.]

797
00:42:34,190 --> 00:42:36,510
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Then I can't use my weapon.]
[Kim Sun Wook: Yeah.]

798
00:42:36,510 --> 00:42:38,670
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
I can't use my weapon even though I have it.]

799
00:42:38,670 --> 00:42:41,760
[Kim Sun Wook: It's a pity then.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I'll feel so wronged.]

800
00:42:41,760 --> 00:42:43,720
[Cho Yun Jae: If we don't talk much even when...]

801
00:42:43,720 --> 00:42:44,920
[Cho Yun Jae: even when we're alone?]

802
00:42:44,920 --> 00:42:46,580
[Cho Yun Jae: We barely talked.]

803
00:42:46,580 --> 00:42:48,700
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
Really? So you just went to bed?]

804
00:42:48,700 --> 00:42:51,700
[Cho Yun Jae: We did talk.
But I think he just isn't talkative.]

805
00:42:51,700 --> 00:42:52,830
[Eum Hyeok Jin: No.]

806
00:42:52,830 --> 00:42:54,870
[Eum Hyeok Jin: He's just a quiet person.]

807
00:42:54,870 --> 00:42:55,180
He's quiet...

808
00:42:55,180 --> 00:42:57,730
[Eum Hyeok Jin: And he gives short responses.]

809
00:42:57,730 --> 00:42:59,020
[Eum Hyeok Jin: He's very composed.]

810
00:42:59,020 --> 00:42:59,340
I think so.

811
00:42:59,340 --> 00:43:01,600
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Doesn't that best describe him?]

812
00:43:02,280 --> 00:43:05,170
[Cho Yun Jae: Yes, you're right.]

813
00:43:06,220 --> 00:43:10,150
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
What do you think about everything?]

814
00:43:10,150 --> 00:43:12,250
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
I want to know your thoughts too.]

815
00:43:12,250 --> 00:43:14,920
[Kim Sun Wook:
Are you guys only going for one person?]

816
00:43:14,920 --> 00:43:18,140
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
No, I'm not just focused on one person.]

817
00:43:18,140 --> 00:43:20,120
[Cho Yun Jae: Really?]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Are you focused on one person?]

818
00:43:20,120 --> 00:43:22,340
[Eum Hyeok Jin: You don't have to do that here.]

819
00:43:22,340 --> 00:43:24,720
[Eum Hyeok Jin: You can explore.]
[Cho Yun Jae: That's true.]

820
00:43:24,720 --> 00:43:28,140
[Cho Yun Jae: But I'm not good at multitasking.]

821
00:43:28,140 --> 00:43:30,190
[Cho Yun Jae: I don't know either, but...]

822
00:43:30,190 --> 00:43:31,510
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
If you're only going for one person,]

823
00:43:31,510 --> 00:43:33,390
[Eum Hyeok Jin: you must be very decisive.]

824
00:43:34,160 --> 00:43:36,040
[Eum Hyeok Jin: It's only a week.]

825
00:43:36,040 --> 00:43:39,720
[Eum Hyeok Jin: If things go badly
on the 6th day, what'd you do?]

826
00:43:39,720 --> 00:43:41,400
[Cho Yun Jae: Oh, really?]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: It could happen.]

827
00:43:41,400 --> 00:43:43,150
But if the person you like...

828
00:43:43,530 --> 00:43:46,740
[Kim Sun Wook: If the person you like
likes someone else,]

829
00:43:46,740 --> 00:43:48,060
[Kim Sun Wook: what would you do?]

830
00:43:49,600 --> 00:43:52,690
[Kim Sun Wook: If you can sense it?]

831
00:43:53,660 --> 00:43:55,690
[Cho Yun Jae: Honestly, I'd give up.]

832
00:43:55,690 --> 00:43:57,730
[Kim Sun Wook: We're so similar.]

833
00:43:57,730 --> 00:43:59,740
[Cho Yun Jae: I'm quite practical...]

834
00:43:59,740 --> 00:44:01,590
[Eum Hyeok Jin: You know me. I won't give up.]

835
00:44:01,920 --> 00:44:05,150
[Kim Sun Wook: I think I'll still
show my interest but not put pressure on him.]

836
00:44:05,150 --> 00:44:08,250
[Eum Hyeok Jin: You can't show your interest
without putting pressure on him.]

837
00:44:08,250 --> 00:44:10,810
[Eum Hyeok Jin: It's contradictory.]
[Cho Yun Jae: It's hard.]

838
00:44:10,810 --> 00:44:12,880
[Kim Sun Wook: It's contradictory,
but I'll still convey my sincerity.]

839
00:44:12,880 --> 00:44:15,020
[Kim Sun Wook: It's not to pressure him]

840
00:44:15,020 --> 00:44:16,820
[Kim Sun Wook: to make a choice.]

841
00:44:16,820 --> 00:44:19,370
[Kim Sun Wook: Just show him what I feel,
and whatever his response is,]

842
00:44:19,370 --> 00:44:21,340
[Kim Sun Wook: I'll respect his decision.]

843
00:44:21,340 --> 00:44:23,730
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Right.]
[Kim Sun Wook: Since he's someone I loved.]

844
00:44:23,730 --> 00:44:26,940
[Kim Sun Wook: I usually
ended all sorts of relationships like this.]

845
00:44:26,940 --> 00:44:29,460
[Cho Yun Jae: What should I do now?]
[Kim Sun Wook: What's wrong?]

846
00:44:29,460 --> 00:44:32,270
[Cho Yun Jae: How should I approach this?]

847
00:44:32,270 --> 00:44:34,080
[Kim Sun Wook: Don't think about it.]
[Cho Yun Jae: Don't think?]

848
00:44:34,080 --> 00:44:36,680
[Kim Sun Wook: Think about it]

849
00:44:36,680 --> 00:44:38,220
[Kim Sun Wook: when it happens.]

850
00:44:38,220 --> 00:44:41,080
[Cho Yun Jae: Oh, yeah?]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: That's one thing.]

851
00:44:41,080 --> 00:44:42,860
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Also, apart from direct]

852
00:44:42,860 --> 00:44:45,460
[Eum Hyeok Jin: flirting and expressions,]

853
00:44:45,460 --> 00:44:49,590
[Eum Hyeok Jin: there is some
really subtle and delicate flirting.]

854
00:44:49,590 --> 00:44:53,960
[Eum Hyeok Jin: More than you think.]
[Kim Sun Wook: Yes, that's important.]

855
00:44:53,960 --> 00:44:55,390
[Eum Hyeok Jin: But sometimes]

856
00:44:55,390 --> 00:44:58,330
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
you might just be misinterpreting things.]

857
00:44:58,330 --> 00:45:01,140
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Really. And...]

858
00:45:01,140 --> 00:45:03,700
[Eum Hyeok Jin: if you had some sparks,]

859
00:45:03,700 --> 00:45:05,560
[Eum Hyeok Jin: whenever he looks at you,]

860
00:45:05,560 --> 00:45:08,140
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
you'll wonder why he keeps looking at you.]

861
00:45:08,140 --> 00:45:10,800
[Eum Hyeok Jin: "Is he flirting?"
You can't help but read into it.]

862
00:45:10,800 --> 00:45:13,020
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Isn't that so?]
[Kim Sun Wook: That's true.]

863
00:45:13,020 --> 00:45:15,870
[Eum Hyeok Jin: That's how it's been for me.]

864
00:45:15,870 --> 00:45:18,980
[Cho Yun Jae:
I thought everyone would go out on dates.]

865
00:45:18,980 --> 00:45:20,630
[Cho Yun Jae: But on the other hand,]

866
00:45:20,630 --> 00:45:25,200
[Cho Yun Jae:
I got to have sincere and honest conversations.]

867
00:45:25,200 --> 00:45:27,850
[Cho Yun Jae: It worked out for the best.]

868
00:45:29,720 --> 00:45:31,980
[Ugh! I'm so fr**king annoyed.]

869
00:45:35,580 --> 00:45:38,910
[Kim Su Min: I've never seen you so conflicted.]

870
00:45:38,910 --> 00:45:40,960
[Park Jae Ha: Whatever.]

871
00:45:44,030 --> 00:45:45,400
[Wary]

872
00:45:46,090 --> 00:45:48,360
[Ah!]

873
00:45:50,760 --> 00:45:52,190
[Kim Su Min: Didn't you two talk?]

874
00:45:52,190 --> 00:45:55,310
[Park Jae Ha: Yes.]

875
00:45:55,310 --> 00:45:57,720
[Park Jae Ha: What's frustrating me is]

876
00:45:57,720 --> 00:46:00,510
[Park Jae Ha:
what Hyeong Jun thinks about doing the reshoot.]

877
00:46:00,510 --> 00:46:02,720
[Park Jae Ha: Since we were dating,]

878
00:46:02,720 --> 00:46:05,680
[Park Jae Ha: we should make a decision together.]

879
00:46:05,680 --> 00:46:07,820
[Park Jae Ha: Hyeong Jun did ask me]

880
00:46:07,820 --> 00:46:10,130
[Park Jae Ha: if I'd do it even if he doesn't.]

881
00:46:10,130 --> 00:46:12,510
[Park Jae Ha: He asked me that.]

882
00:46:12,510 --> 00:46:14,780
[Park Jae Ha: So I said I'd still do the reshoot.]

883
00:46:14,780 --> 00:46:16,710
[Park Jae Ha: Meeting someone great]

884
00:46:16,710 --> 00:46:18,520
[Park Jae Ha: on this show is important to me,]

885
00:46:18,520 --> 00:46:19,770
[Park Jae Ha: but the chance]

886
00:46:19,770 --> 00:46:23,070
[Park Jae Ha: to get to come out publicly]

887
00:46:23,070 --> 00:46:25,800
[Park Jae Ha: did outweigh our relationship.]

888
00:46:26,420 --> 00:46:27,740
[Park Jae Ha: But Hyeong Jun]

889
00:46:27,740 --> 00:46:30,530
[Park Jae Ha: thought it was unnecessary for me]

890
00:46:30,530 --> 00:46:34,860
[Park Jae Ha:
to tell him that my desire to be on the show]

891
00:46:34,860 --> 00:46:37,990
[Park Jae Ha:
is greater than my feelings for him.]

892
00:46:37,990 --> 00:46:39,600
[Park Jae Ha: He said that really hurt him.]

893
00:46:39,600 --> 00:46:43,140
[Park Jae Ha: I only said that because]

894
00:46:43,140 --> 00:46:45,740
[Park Jae Ha: Hyeong Jun and I]

895
00:46:45,740 --> 00:46:47,830
[Park Jae Ha: had talked a lot about coming out]

896
00:46:47,830 --> 00:46:50,400
[Park Jae Ha: and what our families think,]

897
00:46:50,400 --> 00:46:53,580
[Park Jae Ha: so I thought he'd understand.]

898
00:46:53,580 --> 00:46:55,430
[Park Jae Ha: I thought he'd know]

899
00:46:55,430 --> 00:46:57,570
[Park Jae Ha: how I'm feeling.]

900
00:46:57,570 --> 00:47:01,990
[Park Jae Ha: But he took it differently.]

901
00:47:02,470 --> 00:47:03,770
[Park Jae Ha: Of course I'm sorry.]

902
00:47:03,770 --> 00:47:06,810
[Park Jae Ha: So I apologized to him.]

903
00:47:07,490 --> 00:47:09,960
[Kim Su Min: You have totally different ideas.]

904
00:47:09,960 --> 00:47:11,580
[Park Jae Ha: Yeah, we do.]

905
00:47:12,220 --> 00:47:14,590
[Park Jae Ha: Ugh, I'm so annoyed.]

906
00:47:14,590 --> 00:47:17,000
[Kim Su Min: You need to
make him feel like he can trust you again.]

907
00:47:17,000 --> 00:47:18,470
[Kim Su Min: In my opinion.]

908
00:47:19,140 --> 00:47:22,660
[Park Jae Ha: It's not easy. Really.]

909
00:47:24,830 --> 00:47:28,060
[Park Jae Ha: What about you?]

910
00:47:28,060 --> 00:47:30,970
[Park Jae Ha:
Is the person who returned your call on a date?]

911
00:47:30,970 --> 00:47:33,790
[Kim Su Min: Right now?]
[Park Jae Ha: Yeah.]

912
00:47:33,790 --> 00:47:34,820
[Kim Su Min: No.]

913
00:47:34,820 --> 00:47:37,900
[Park Jae Ha: It's someone here?]
[Kim Su Min: Yeah.]

914
00:47:37,900 --> 00:47:40,010
[Thinking]

915
00:47:40,010 --> 00:47:42,110
[Park Jae Ha: Did you really call Sun Wook?]

916
00:47:43,030 --> 00:47:45,070
[Kim Su Min: Yeah.]

917
00:47:47,380 --> 00:47:48,510
[Kim Su Min: But I think]

918
00:47:48,510 --> 00:47:51,440
[Kim Su Min: it got more awkward after the call.]

919
00:47:51,440 --> 00:47:54,170
[Park Jae Ha: Why would it get awkward?]

920
00:47:54,170 --> 00:47:59,230
[Kim Su Min: I'm not good at opening up]

921
00:47:59,230 --> 00:48:02,150
[Kim Su Min: and expressing my feelings.]

922
00:48:02,150 --> 00:48:04,400
[Kim Su Min:
I don't think I conveyed my feelings well.]

923
00:48:04,400 --> 00:48:06,040
[Kim Su Min: That's the main reason.]

924
00:48:06,040 --> 00:48:10,260
[Kim Su Min: Since I'm not confident.]

925
00:48:10,260 --> 00:48:14,070
[Kim Su Min:
I really want to be assertive, you know?]

926
00:48:14,070 --> 00:48:15,670
[Park Jae Ha: But you can't?]

927
00:48:16,310 --> 00:48:18,950
[Park Jae Ha: Well, it's not easy.]

928
00:48:18,950 --> 00:48:21,180
[Park Jae Ha:
It doesn't come naturally for everyone.]

929
00:48:21,180 --> 00:48:23,660
[Kim Su Min: Although I liked Sun Wook before,]

930
00:48:23,660 --> 00:48:27,040
[Kim Su Min: I just
watched him from afar and took care of him.]

931
00:48:27,040 --> 00:48:28,980
[Kim Su Min: Nothing more.]

932
00:48:28,980 --> 00:48:33,180
[Kim Su Min: If I suddenly
become proactive after the call...]

933
00:48:33,780 --> 00:48:35,450
[Kim Su Min: I should just tell him all these.]

934
00:48:35,450 --> 00:48:37,350
[Kim Su Min: But after talking...]

935
00:48:39,500 --> 00:48:40,770
[Kim Su Min: I don't know.]

936
00:48:40,770 --> 00:48:43,700
[Kim Su Min: I don't know how I feel as well.]

937
00:48:43,700 --> 00:48:45,730
[Park Jae Ha: Bring him here.]

938
00:48:45,730 --> 00:48:47,870
[Park Jae Ha: I'll go to another room.]

939
00:48:47,870 --> 00:48:54,100
[Park Jae Ha: Sun Wook must be with others there.]
[Kim Su Min: Yeah.]

940
00:48:54,100 --> 00:48:57,450
[Park Jae Ha: I think this is your chance.]

941
00:48:57,450 --> 00:48:59,110
[Park Jae Ha: I just talked to Hyeong Jun too.]

942
00:48:59,110 --> 00:49:02,140
[Park Jae Ha: No matter how I thought about it,
it felt like my only chance.]

943
00:49:02,140 --> 00:49:04,180
[Park Jae Ha: Some will be on dates later.]

944
00:49:04,180 --> 00:49:05,850
[Park Jae Ha: We don't know who,]

945
00:49:05,850 --> 00:49:07,710
[Park Jae Ha: but it could be Hyeong Jun.]

946
00:49:07,710 --> 00:49:10,790
[Park Jae Ha: So it was now or never.]

947
00:49:10,790 --> 00:49:13,930
[Park Jae Ha: That's why I asked to talk to him.]

948
00:49:13,930 --> 00:49:17,430
[Park Jae Ha: And we went to talk in private.]

949
00:49:20,980 --> 00:49:23,930
[Kim Su Min: Let me sort out my thoughts alone.]
[Park Jae Ha: To find your courage? Sure.]

950
00:49:23,930 --> 00:49:25,290
[Kim Su Min: Sort out my thoughts.]
[Park Jae Ha: I'll leave.]

951
00:49:26,870 --> 00:49:28,150
[Park Jae Ha: Wow, this is fun.]

952
00:49:28,150 --> 00:49:31,850
[Park Jae Ha: I don't know why I'm so happy
when things are bad for me too.]

953
00:49:33,100 --> 00:49:36,080
[Kim Su Min: Go on. I'll see you later.]
[Park Jae Ha: OK.]

954
00:49:40,140 --> 00:49:42,830
[Kim Su Min: Because
I haven't figured out what I wanted to say,]

955
00:49:42,830 --> 00:49:46,920
[Kim Su Min: I couldn't go straight to him.]

956
00:49:46,920 --> 00:49:49,910
[Kim Su Min: I was alone, thinking,]

957
00:49:49,910 --> 00:49:52,070
[Kim Su Min: "Should I say it like this or that?"]

958
00:49:52,070 --> 00:49:54,670
[Kim Su Min: "Do I bring it up like this or that?"]

959
00:49:54,670 --> 00:49:57,040
[Kim Su Min: I thought about it a lot,]

960
00:49:57,040 --> 00:49:59,410
[Kim Su Min: for about 5 to 10 minutes.]

961
00:50:02,850 --> 00:50:04,500
[Kim Su Min: And my conclusion was...]

962
00:50:04,500 --> 00:50:09,110
["Just speak from your heart."]

963
00:50:09,900 --> 00:50:13,550
[Su Min plucks up the courage to find Sun Wook]

964
00:50:14,180 --> 00:50:16,180
[What will Su Min say to Sun Wook?]

965
00:50:16,590 --> 00:50:19,540
[Kim Su Min: Ah, it's cold.]

966
00:50:19,540 --> 00:50:22,490
[Park Jae Ha: Aren't you cold?]
[Kim Su Min: I'm cold.]

967
00:50:22,490 --> 00:50:25,230
[Kim Su Min: It was warm when the sun was out.]

968
00:50:25,230 --> 00:50:27,220
[Park Jae Ha:
The temperature drops a lot after the sunset.]

969
00:50:28,760 --> 00:50:30,810
[Cho Yun Jae: Right, that's changed.]

970
00:50:32,490 --> 00:50:35,040
[Park Jae Ha: Just doodling.
Since there's nothing to do.]

971
00:50:35,040 --> 00:50:38,890
[Kim Su Min: Shall we talk?]
[Kim Sun Wook: OK.]

972
00:50:38,890 --> 00:50:40,510
[Kim Su Min: Let's go to my room.]

973
00:50:43,130 --> 00:50:47,440
[Kim Su Min: We should've gone for a drive.]
[Kim Sun Wook: I know.]

974
00:50:51,900 --> 00:50:57,590
[Su Min & Sun Wook get some time alone]

975
00:51:00,080 --> 00:51:04,870
[Kim Su Min: Please come in.]

976
00:51:08,420 --> 00:51:10,360
[Kim Sun Wook: So clean.]

977
00:51:12,300 --> 00:51:14,740
[Kim Sun Wook: Ah, it's cold.]

978
00:51:16,480 --> 00:51:19,160
[Kim Su Min:
Before I called you yesterday, I was really torn.]

979
00:51:19,160 --> 00:51:21,840
[Kim Sun Wook: I see.]

980
00:51:21,840 --> 00:51:24,120
[Kim Su Min:
I felt different when I saw you again yesterday.]

981
00:51:24,120 --> 00:51:26,400
[Kim Sun Wook: I see.]

982
00:51:26,400 --> 00:51:31,360
[Kim Su Min: I did a lot of thinking
while walking to the Phone Room, and...]

983
00:51:32,600 --> 00:51:35,640
[Kim Su Min: I thought I should follow my heart.]

984
00:51:35,640 --> 00:51:38,680
[Kim Su Min: So I called you.]
[Kim Sun Wook: I see.]

985
00:51:38,680 --> 00:51:43,100
[Kim Su Min: I wanted to call you yesterday.]

986
00:51:43,100 --> 00:51:45,030
[Kim Sun Wook: I also...]

987
00:51:47,120 --> 00:51:49,560
[Kim Sun Wook: I could tell that.]

988
00:51:49,900 --> 00:51:52,090
[Kim Sun Wook: I didn't expect to get your call.]

989
00:51:52,090 --> 00:51:56,460
[Kim Sun Wook: But I did think about it.]

990
00:51:58,360 --> 00:52:01,280
[Kim Sun Wook:
More than half of us are returning participants]

991
00:52:01,280 --> 00:52:05,010
[Kim Sun Wook:
who've all become friendly with each other.]

992
00:52:05,010 --> 00:52:08,560
[Kim Sun Wook:
So on the first day, I felt a lot of pressure]

993
00:52:08,560 --> 00:52:10,940
[Kim Sun Wook: about the calls and whatnot.]

994
00:52:10,940 --> 00:52:14,700
[Kim Sun Wook: But rather than first impressions]

995
00:52:14,700 --> 00:52:18,080
[Kim Sun Wook: or appearances,]

996
00:52:19,010 --> 00:52:22,310
[Kim Sun Wook: your sincerity touched me more.]

997
00:52:22,310 --> 00:52:25,960
[Kim Sun Wook: That's why I wanted to
express my feelings in that way,]

998
00:52:25,960 --> 00:52:27,670
[Kim Sun Wook: to express my gratitude.]

999
00:52:27,670 --> 00:52:30,590
[Kim Sun Wook: I did want to call you yesterday.]

1000
00:52:31,420 --> 00:52:33,900
[Kim Su Min: When I got your call, I was...]
[Kim Sun Wook: Surprised, right?]

1001
00:52:34,230 --> 00:52:35,860
[Kim Su Min: Very surprised.]
[Kim Sun Wook: Right?]

1002
00:52:35,860 --> 00:52:37,600
[Kim Sun Wook:
Everyone in this room must've been surprised.]

1003
00:52:37,940 --> 00:52:41,270
[Kim Su Min: No one knows.]
[Kim Sun Wook: Really? Still?]

1004
00:52:42,110 --> 00:52:43,910
[Kim Su Min: Almost no one knows.]

1005
00:52:43,910 --> 00:52:46,750
[Kim Sun Wook: Really?
I saw you from the Phone Room.]

1006
00:52:46,750 --> 00:52:48,120
[Kim Sun Wook:
I was looking at you during the call.]

1007
00:52:48,120 --> 00:52:49,500
[Kim Su Min: Really?]

1008
00:52:49,500 --> 00:52:51,790
[Kim Sun Wook: Yeah, I copied your "Hello"]

1009
00:52:51,790 --> 00:52:54,640
[Kim Sun Wook: while looking at you.]

1010
00:52:54,640 --> 00:52:56,250
[Kim Sun Wook: I could see you from there.]

1011
00:52:56,250 --> 00:52:59,010
[Kim Sun Wook: So I thought
you were looking at the Phone Room.]

1012
00:52:59,010 --> 00:53:02,690
[Kim Su Min: I had no idea.
And I was so surprised when you called me.]

1013
00:53:02,690 --> 00:53:05,900
[Kim Sun Wook: I was most grateful to you]

1014
00:53:05,900 --> 00:53:09,830
[Kim Sun Wook:
and you were the most memorable one yesterday.]

1015
00:53:11,890 --> 00:53:17,150
[Kim Su Min: I'm really slow to warm up.]

1016
00:53:17,150 --> 00:53:19,590
[Kim Su Min: People around me know,]

1017
00:53:19,590 --> 00:53:24,490
[Kim Su Min: but it's hard for me
to express my feelings.]

1018
00:53:25,600 --> 00:53:27,490
[Kim Su Min: It's not easy for me.]

1019
00:53:27,490 --> 00:53:30,680
[Kim Su Min: When I called you yesterday,]

1020
00:53:30,680 --> 00:53:34,210
[Kim Su Min: the text said
to call the one you're drawn to,]

1021
00:53:34,210 --> 00:53:35,400
[Kim Su Min: so I...]

1022
00:53:35,400 --> 00:53:40,030
[Kim Su Min: I know I'm drawn to you right now.]

1023
00:53:45,490 --> 00:53:49,680
["I'm going to keep expressing my feelings…"]

1024
00:53:53,140 --> 00:53:57,970
[Kim Su Min: By my own standards,
I think I've put a lot of effort into you.]

1025
00:53:57,970 --> 00:54:00,460
[Kim Sun Wook: I can sense that.]

1026
00:54:00,460 --> 00:54:03,020
[Kim Su Min: As someone slow to warm up,]

1027
00:54:03,020 --> 00:54:05,570
[Kim Su Min:
it took every ounce of my courage to do this.]

1028
00:54:09,420 --> 00:54:11,730
[Kim Sun Wook: Putting aside
being slow to warm up,]

1029
00:54:11,730 --> 00:54:14,850
[Kim Sun Wook: I know how hard it is]

1030
00:54:14,850 --> 00:54:17,400
[Kim Sun Wook: to express your feelings.]

1031
00:54:18,090 --> 00:54:24,140
[Kim Sun Wook: It's not easy.]

1032
00:54:24,140 --> 00:54:26,810
[Kim Sun Wook: The fact that you said all these,]

1033
00:54:26,810 --> 00:54:29,390
[Kim Sun Wook: I'm sure it took a lot of courage.
I felt it right away.]

1034
00:54:29,390 --> 00:54:31,790
[Kim Sun Wook: Because I know you.]

1035
00:54:31,790 --> 00:54:35,120
[Kim Sun Wook:
I know how hard it is to say these things.]

1036
00:54:36,920 --> 00:54:40,630
[Kim Sun Wook: But if...]

1037
00:54:40,630 --> 00:54:43,820
[Kim Sun Wook: There's more people now,]

1038
00:54:43,820 --> 00:54:46,170
[Kim Sun Wook: and we still have a lot of time.]

1039
00:54:49,140 --> 00:54:54,920
["I'm worried about getting hurt too."]

1040
00:54:59,340 --> 00:55:03,860
[Kim Su Min: I don't know if this is one-sided,]

1041
00:55:03,860 --> 00:55:08,470
[Kim Su Min: but I hope you don't feel pressured.]

1042
00:55:11,600 --> 00:55:13,560
[Kim Su Min: He totally understood]

1043
00:55:13,560 --> 00:55:17,230
[Kim Su Min: how much it took for me to]

1044
00:55:17,230 --> 00:55:20,030
[Kim Su Min: say all these to him.]

1045
00:55:20,030 --> 00:55:23,700
[Kim Su Min:
I realized he does know a bit about how I feel.]

1046
00:55:23,700 --> 00:55:29,100
[Kim Su Min: I plan to express myself more.]

1047
00:55:35,880 --> 00:55:38,810
["Let's go out on a date."]

1048
00:55:38,810 --> 00:55:41,720
[Kim Sun Wook: A proper date?]

1049
00:55:41,720 --> 00:55:47,810
[Kim Su Min: Give me a chance too.]
[Kim Sun Wook: OK.]

1050
00:55:52,120 --> 00:55:55,150
["Let's do it."]

1051
00:55:58,830 --> 00:56:03,590
[Su Min's love conveyed with courage & sincerity,
will it come to fruition?]

1052
00:56:04,290 --> 00:56:08,940
-Block A?
-Yeah? Let's go. It's more comfortable.

1053
00:56:08,940 --> 00:56:11,220
[Eum Hyeok Jin: The 2nd floor is so nice.]

1054
00:56:11,220 --> 00:56:15,160
[Eum Hyeok Jin: The floor-to-ceiling windows]

1055
00:56:15,160 --> 00:56:16,860
[Eum Hyeok Jin: make it more open.]

1056
00:56:17,820 --> 00:56:19,640
[Cho Yun Jae: Should I sleep on the sofa tonight?]

1057
00:56:19,640 --> 00:56:23,570
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Is it that serious?]
[Park Jae Ha: Oh, come on.]

1058
00:56:23,570 --> 00:56:25,440
[Cho Yun Jae: No, no.]
[Park Jae Ha: There's no bedding here.]

1059
00:56:25,440 --> 00:56:27,900
[Park Jae Ha: You'll bring the bedding out?]
[Cho Yun Jae: Yeah.]

1060
00:56:27,900 --> 00:56:30,200
[Park Jae Ha: Oh, come on.]
[Cho Yun Jae: I'm doing it for my own convenience.]

1061
00:56:30,200 --> 00:56:30,810
[Hyeok Jin comes to Han Gyeol's room]

1062
00:56:30,810 --> 00:56:32,270
Convenience? Oh, please.

1063
00:56:32,820 --> 00:56:36,440
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I wrote a note in my room.]

1064
00:56:36,440 --> 00:56:40,850
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
"I wanted to ask you out during the day,"]

1065
00:56:40,850 --> 00:56:44,090
[Eum Hyeok Jin: "but it was a pity that I couldn't.
I hope I get to talk to you next time."]

1066
00:56:44,090 --> 00:56:47,240
[Eum Hyeok Jin: When I went up, no one was there.]

1067
00:56:47,240 --> 00:56:50,100
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
The bag he brought on the first day was open]

1068
00:56:50,100 --> 00:56:51,790
[Eum Hyeok Jin: with his stuff still inside.]

1069
00:56:51,790 --> 00:56:53,560
[Eum Hyeok Jin: So I guess he always]

1070
