[Park Jae Ha: You keep looking for Hyeok Jin.]

1075
00:57:07,780 --> 00:57:10,390
[Cho Yun Jae: I'm just curious where he is.]
[Park Jae Ha: You keep looking for Hyeok Jin.]

1076
00:57:10,390 --> 00:57:12,050
[Cho Yun Jae: I'm just curious where he is.]

1077
00:57:12,050 --> 00:57:14,330
