1078
00:57:14,330 --> 00:57:15,480
[Park Jae Ha: Must be the bathroom.]

1079
00:57:15,480 --> 00:57:17,230
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Why? Looking for me?]

1080
00:57:17,230 --> 00:57:20,850
[Cho Yun Jae: I was looking for you again.]
[Park Jae Ha: Yun Jae was looking for you.]

1081
00:57:20,850 --> 00:57:22,080
[Park Jae Ha: He keeps looking for you.]

1082
00:57:22,080 --> 00:57:24,610
[Park Jae Ha:
Like a puppy with separation anxiety.]

1083
00:57:24,610 --> 00:57:25,310
