1084
00:57:25,640 --> 00:57:27,220
[Park Jae Ha: This is separation anxiety.]

1085
00:57:27,220 --> 00:57:29,960
[Cho Yun Jae: Because we came in together
but you suddenly disappeared.]

1086
00:57:29,960 --> 00:57:34,020
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Go on with your business.]

1087
00:57:34,020 --> 00:57:36,700
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I was dealing with my stuff too.]
