1088
00:57:36,700 --> 00:57:38,270
[Park Jae Ha: You have a lot to do alone, huh?]

1089
00:57:38,270 --> 00:57:40,180
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I've been busy since before dawn.]

1090
00:57:40,180 --> 00:57:42,290
[Park Jae Ha: What do you have to do?]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I don't know.]

1091
00:57:42,290 --> 00:57:45,580
[Park Jae Ha: You're so busy.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I'm really busy.]

1092
00:57:45,580 --> 00:57:48,670
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I'm doing
