[Cho Yun Jae: So proactive... So cool.]

1094
00:57:52,100 --> 00:57:53,540
[Shy]

1095
00:57:53,850 --> 00:57:55,000
[Cho Yun Jae: No, seriously.]

1096
00:57:55,940 --> 00:57:58,000
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
It's most comfortable to chat here, right?]

1097
00:57:58,000 --> 00:58:02,480
[Park Jae Ha: Yeah, lounging around all relaxed.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: It feels more casual.]

1098
00:58:02,480 --> 00:58:04,960
[Cho Yun Jae: The right time, place,
and occasion really matters.]

1099
00:58:04,960 --> 00:58:05,890
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Yeah.]

1100
00:58:06,380 --> 00:58:08,570
[Park Jae Ha: Have you felt]

1101
00:58:08,570 --> 00:58:11,630
[Park Jae Ha: any sparks with your...]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: No.]

1102
00:58:11,630 --> 00:58:13,220
[Park Jae Ha: Are you waiting for it?]

1103
00:58:13,220 --> 00:58:15,450
[Park Jae Ha:
You can create situations to speed things up.]

1104
00:58:15,450 --> 00:58:17,690
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I did try today.]

1105
00:58:17,690 --> 00:58:22,760
[Eum Hyeok Jin: But it failed.]
[Park Jae Ha: I see.]

1106
00:58:22,760 --> 00:58:23,970
[Eum Hyeok Jin: It failed.]

1107
00:58:23,970 --> 00:58:26,870
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Not in terms of sparks,]

1108
00:58:26,870 --> 00:58:29,970
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
but that I failed to carry out my plan.]

1109
00:58:29,970 --> 00:58:31,920
[Park Jae Ha: Oh... the toast?]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: No.]

1110
00:58:32,250 --> 00:58:34,580
[Eum Hyeok Jin: The toast was for everyone,
since it's the first day.]

1111
00:58:34,580 --> 00:58:36,000
[Park Jae Ha: I see.]
[Cho Yun Jae: It was delicious.]

1112
00:58:36,000 --> 00:58:39,390
[Park Jae Ha: He's a good cook.]
[Cho Yun Jae: You can start a business.]

1113
00:58:39,390 --> 00:58:40,720
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I'm a good cook.]

1114
00:58:40,720 --> 00:58:43,440
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
I like to cook for the person I like.]

1115
00:58:43,540 --> 00:58:45,820
[Park Jae Ha:
Me too. I like to do things for them.]

1116
00:58:45,820 --> 00:58:49,150
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
I'm happy to see them eat well.]

1117
00:58:49,150 --> 00:58:51,150
[Eum Hyeok Jin: For you...]
[Cho Yun Jae: Yeah?]

1118
00:58:51,150 --> 00:58:56,170
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Are you not interested in
