1119
00:58:56,170 --> 00:58:59,560
[Cho Yun Jae: To be really honest, it's you.]

1120
00:58:59,560 --> 00:59:01,060
[(Jae Ha)-hyung.]

1121
00:59:01,060 --> 00:59:01,560
[Really?]

1122
00:59:01,560 --> 00:59:07,220
[Cho Yun Jae: Because when he speaks, he's...
I don't know, good at carrying a conversation.]

1123
00:59:07,220 --> 00:59:10,360
[Cho Yun Jae: That's what I thought.
On the first day,]

1124
00:59:10,360 --> 00:59:14,440
[Cho Yun Jae:
I thought he was good at leading things.]

1125
00:59:14,440 --> 00:59:16,130
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Do you like people like that?]

1126
00:59:16,590 --> 00:59:17,840
[Nods]

1127
00:59:17,840 --> 00:59:18,840
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Someone who leads?]

1128
00:59:18,840 --> 00:59:22,660
[Cho Yun Jae:
I thought it might be fun to be around him.]

1129
00:59:23,990 --> 00:59:27,160
[Cho Yun Jae: But saying it here is so awkward.]

1130
00:59:27,160 --> 00:59:28,520
[Eum Hyeok Jin: No, actually...]

1131
00:59:28,520 --> 00:59:31,130
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
Being straightforward is a good approach.]

1132
00:59:31,130 --> 00:59:33,740
[Park Jae Ha: Yeah.]

1133
00:59:33,740 --> 00:59:38,640
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I just feel a bit left out.]

1134
00:59:38,640 --> 00:59:42,590
[Shy]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Should I leave you two to talk?]

1135
00:59:47,300 --> 00:59:52,230
