1136
00:59:55,020 --> 00:59:56,850
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Back already?]
[Park Jae Ha: So soon.]

1137
00:59:56,850 --> 00:59:58,240
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Really soon.]

1138
00:59:59,670 --> 01:00:01,620
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Where'd you go?]
[Lee Hyun Jun: The zoo.]

1139
01:00:01,620 --> 01:00:03,560
[Eum Hyeok Jin: The zoo?]
[Lee Hyun Jun: Yeah.]

1140
01:00:03,560 --> 01:00:05,460
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Indoor or outdoor zoo?]

1141
01:00:05,460 --> 01:00:08,510
[Kim Han Gyeol: Outdoor. We saw everything.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: It must've been cold.]

1142
01:00:08,510 --> 01:00:08,540
What did you see?

1143
01:00:08,540 --> 01:00:10,000
[Park Jae Ha:
Were you three together the whole date?]

1144
01:00:10,000 --> 01:00:10,780
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Yeah.]

1145
01:00:10,780 --> 01:00:11,930
[Eum Hyeok Jin: What did you see?]

1146
01:00:11,930 --> 01:00:14,790
[Kim Han Gyeol: Lions, tigers, capybaras, bears.]
[Lee Hyeok Jin: A lot.]

1147
01:00:14,790 --> 01:00:16,390
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Capybaras are cute.]
[Kim Han Gyeol: And ostriches.]

1148
01:00:16,390 --> 01:00:18,200
[Lee Hyeok Jin: But the capybara didn't come out.]

1149
01:00:18,610 --> 01:00:22,790
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Walk out?]
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Yeah.]

1150
01:00:22,790 --> 01:00:25,740
[Cho Yun Jae:
You didn't get to eat cotton candy then?]

1151
01:00:25,740 --> 01:00:29,580
[Kim Han Gyeol: It was too cold for that.]
[Cho Yun Jae: Oh, wrong weather.]

1152
01:00:30,200 --> 01:00:32,720
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Should you be idling around?]

1153
01:00:32,720 --> 01:00:34,180
[Eum Hyeok Jin: You should move your stuff.]

1154
01:00:34,180 --> 01:00:35,910
[Kim Han Gyeol:
The clothing rack hasn't arrived.]

1155
01:00:35,910 --> 01:00:38,330
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Oh, a rack?]
[Kim Han Gyeol: Yeah.]

1156
01:00:38,330 --> 01:00:40,290
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Oh! I think I saw it.]
[Kim Han Gyeol: A rack?]

1157
01:00:40,290 --> 01:00:40,850
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Yeah.]

1158
