[Kim Han Gyeol: Are you feeling OK?]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Hmm?]

1169
01:01:25,890 --> 01:01:30,240
[Kim Han Gyeol: Are you OK?]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I'm just a little tired.]

1170
01:01:32,790 --> 01:01:38,360
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I usually sleep well.]
[Kim Han Gyeol: I see.]

1171
01:01:38,360 --> 01:01:42,160
[Eum Hyeok Jin: But I didn't sleep well today.]

1172
01:01:42,160 --> 01:01:45,970
[Kim Han Gyeol:
But the toast at breakfast was really good.]

1173
01:01:45,970 --> 01:01:48,460
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Thanks for enjoying it.]

1174
01:01:48,460 --> 01:01:53,300
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I was only
