1177
01:02:06,580 --> 01:02:08,290
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Do you like paintings?]

1178
01:02:08,290 --> 01:02:10,900
[Kim Han Gyeol: Paintings? Occasionally?]

1179
01:02:10,900 --> 01:02:13,030
[Kim Han Gyeol: But compared to paintings,]

1180
01:02:13,030 --> 01:02:14,920
[Kim Han Gyeol:
I prefer traveling to places like this.]

1181
01:02:14,920 --> 01:02:17,670
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Galleries?]
[Kim Han Gyeol: Yes, galleries.]

1182
01:02:17,670 --> 01:02:20,660
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
I used to go to take photos a lot.]

1183
01:02:20,660 --> 01:02:22,120
Take photos of paintings.

1184
01:02:22,340 --> 01:02:26,450
[Kim Han Gyeol:
Once, I went to Atrium with an ex.]

1185
01:02:26,450 --> 01:02:29,720
[Kim Han Gyeol:
It was my first time. It was fun.]

1186
01:02:29,720 --> 01:02:32,940
[Kim Han Gyeol: Do you like traveling?]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I haven't traveled in a long time.]

1187
01:02:32,940 --> 01:02:34,370
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I used to prefer]

1188
01:02:34,370 --> 01:02:36,210
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
spending money elsewhere, like on clothes.]

1189
01:02:36,210 --> 01:02:40,700
[Eum Hyeok Jin: But now that I'm older,
I find traveling necessary.]

1190
01:02:40,700 --> 01:02:44,230
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
So I go to Busan alone. And stuff.]

1191
01:02:44,230 --> 01:02:48,570
[Kim Han Gyeol: Instead of a few small trips,
I like to save up for a bigger trip.]

1192
01:02:48,570 --> 01:02:51,970
[Kim Han Gyeol: Like touring Europe alone.]

1193
01:02:51,970 --> 01:02:56,680
[Eum Hyeok Jin: For me, since I'm a model,]

1194
01:02:56,680 --> 01:02:59,910
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
when I go to Milan and Paris, after Fashion Week,]

1195
01:02:59,910 --> 01:03:01,590
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I get to stay for a while.]

1196
01:03:01,590 --> 01:03:04,400
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
That's when I go look around a bit.]

1197
01:03:04,400 --> 01:03:06,630
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
But I never saw it as real traveling.]

1198
01:03:06,630 --> 01:03:09,140
[Kim Han Gyeol: I really like Milan.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Really?]

1199
01:03:09,140 --> 01:03:12,570
[Kim Han Gyeol: But... When I went to Italy,]

1200
01:03:12,570 --> 01:03:14,750
[Kim Han Gyeol:
North, Central, and South of Italy,]

1201
01:03:14,750 --> 01:03:15,970
[Kim Han Gyeol: I liked Milan the most.]

1202
01:03:15,970 --> 01:03:17,760
[Kim Han Gyeol: So, how should I put it?]

1203
01:03:17,760 --> 01:03:20,850
[Kim Han Gyeol: When you first
introduced yourself, you mentioned Milan.]

1204
01:03:20,850 --> 01:03:25,120
[Kim Han Gyeol:
I really wanted to say it's so cool.]

1205
01:03:25,120 --> 01:03:26,200
So…

1206
01:03:26,340 --> 01:03:28,960
[Kim Han Gyeol: But staying here is really...]

1207
01:03:28,960 --> 01:03:31,790
[Kim Han Gyeol: I'm immersed in dopamine.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Why?]

1208
01:03:31,790 --> 01:03:38,180
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Apart from
the people who's shown interest in you,]

1209
01:03:38,180 --> 01:03:43,100
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
are you curious about or interested]

1210
01:03:43,100 --> 01:03:45,080
[Eum Hyeok Jin: in anyone?]
[Kim Han Gyeol: You.]

1211
01:03:45,080 --> 01:03:48,700
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Me? Why?]
[Kim Han Gyeol: I like]

1212
01:03:48,700 --> 01:03:52,910
[Kim Han Gyeol:
people who are responsive and cheerful.]

1213
01:03:52,910 --> 01:03:56,270
[Kim Han Gyeol:
And I personally think you're very cool.]

1214
01:03:56,270 --> 01:03:58,140
[Kim Han Gyeol: There's not many people.]

1215
01:03:58,140 --> 01:04:01,320
[Kim Han Gyeol: You are one of
two or three guys I'm interested in.]

1216
01:04:01,320 --> 01:04:04,510
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Really?]

1217
01:04:04,510 --> 01:04:07,360
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I'm very drawn to him.]

1218
01:04:07,360 --> 01:04:10,310
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I'm intrigued.
I want to know more about him.]

1219
01:04:14,860 --> 01:04:16,780
[Hyeong Jun]

1220
01:04:16,780 --> 01:04:20,740
[Hyeong Jun & Taichi]

1221
01:04:20,740 --> 01:04:21,550
[Hyeong Jun & Taichi & Min Seong
are back at the dorm]

1222
01:04:21,550 --> 01:04:22,720
Thank you.

1223
01:04:27,920 --> 01:04:30,070
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Is there anyone you're drawn to?]

1224
01:04:30,070 --> 01:04:32,040
[Taichi: Yes, I don't know if I'm drawn to him,]

1225
01:04:32,040 --> 01:04:33,310
[Taichi: but I want to go on a date with him.]

1226
01:04:33,310 --> 01:04:34,130
Go on a date?

1227
01:04:34,480 --> 01:04:38,120
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Han Gyeol, right?]
[Taichi: I'm not saying.]

1228
01:04:38,120 --> 01:04:39,390
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Right.]

1229
01:04:39,390 --> 01:04:40,910
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
He hasn't gone on a date with Han Gyeol, right?]

1230
01:04:40,910 --> 01:04:41,650
Yeah.

1231
01:04:42,250 --> 01:04:45,460
[Taichi: But there's someone I want to date.]
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Someone you like?]

1232
01:04:45,460 --> 01:04:47,350
[Taichi: I'm not sure yet.]

1233
01:04:47,350 --> 01:04:50,260
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Just curious about him?]
[Taichi: Yeah.]

1234
01:04:50,260 --> 01:04:53,350
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Right now,
isn't everyone more at the stage of curiosity?]

1235
01:04:53,350 --> 01:04:54,920
[Eum Hyeok Jin: It's more likely.]

1236
01:04:54,920 --> 01:04:58,780
[Taichi: What about you?]
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Me?]

1237
01:04:58,780 --> 01:05:01,260
[Taichi: You were sure before.]
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Yeah.]

1238
01:05:01,260 --> 01:05:05,020
[Taichi: Are you sure this time too?]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Right, I'm curious if]

1239
01:05:05,020 --> 01:05:08,670
[Eum Hyeok Jin: after today's date,]

1240
01:05:08,670 --> 01:05:11,140
[Eum Hyeok Jin: did you become more confused]

1241
01:05:11,140 --> 01:05:14,110
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
or did you realize who you like more?]

1242
01:05:14,400 --> 01:05:15,730
[Lee Hyeok Jin: It's not the latter.]

1243
01:05:15,730 --> 01:05:19,460
[Lee Hyeok Jin: I don't think it clarifies much.]

1244
01:05:19,460 --> 01:05:23,210
[Lee Hyeok Jin:
Earlier, I called Hyun Jun aside and directly]

1245
01:05:23,210 --> 01:05:25,430
[Lee Hyeok Jin:
told him I wanted to go on a date with him.]

1246
01:05:25,430 --> 01:05:27,290
[Lee Hyeok Jin:
It's our second time on the show,]

1247
01:05:27,290 --> 01:05:29,090
[Lee Hyeok Jin: and I told him]

1248
01:05:29,100 --> 01:05:32,640
[Lee Hyeok Jin:
I want to pick things up from where I left off.]

1249
01:05:32,640 --> 01:05:34,110
[Taichi: For you, it's a chance.]

1250
01:05:34,110 --> 01:05:35,450
[Taichi: Since he...]

1251
01:05:35,450 --> 01:05:36,900
[Taichi: Since it didn't work out last time.]

1252
01:05:36,900 --> 01:05:39,050
[Lee Hyeok Jin:
Yeah, so it's an opportunity for me.

1253
01:05:39,050 --> 01:05:41,210
[Lee Hyeok Jin:
So I said I wanted to go on a date,]

1254
01:05:41,210 --> 01:05:43,330
[Lee Hyeok Jin:
but I ended up on a trio date again.]

1255
01:05:43,330 --> 01:05:45,780
[Lee Hyeok Jin:
What could I've done in this situation?]

1256
01:05:45,780 --> 01:05:48,000
[Lee Hyeok Jin: If I show more interest to one,]

1257
01:05:48,000 --> 01:05:49,340
[Lee Hyeok Jin: the other is neglected.]

1258
01:05:49,340 --> 01:05:51,380
[Eum Hyeok Jin: If you really know]

1259
01:05:51,380 --> 01:05:53,880
[Eum Hyeok Jin: who you prefer]

1260
01:05:53,880 --> 01:05:56,670
[Eum Hyeok Jin: and lock in on him,]

1261
01:05:56,670 --> 01:05:58,800
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
I don't think it's wrong to do that.]

1262
01:05:58,800 --> 01:06:01,200
[Lee Hyeok Jin: I'd feel so bad.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: It's normal to feel bad.]

1263
01:06:01,200 --> 01:06:04,230
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
But it's fine to do that on this show.]

1264
01:06:01,200 --> 01:06:01,200
If you feel bad...

1265
01:06:04,230 --> 01:06:05,970
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Because, let's say]

1266
01:06:05,970 --> 01:06:09,300
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
in this situation, some new guy suddenly]

1267
01:06:09,300 --> 01:06:10,720
[Eum Hyeok Jin: confesses to you.]

1268
01:06:10,720 --> 01:06:13,070
[Eum Hyeok Jin: So what if you feel bad?
Wouldn't you still pick Hyun Jun?]

1269
01:06:13,070 --> 01:06:14,380
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
It's the same thing. It's fine in this setting.]

1270
01:06:14,380 --> 01:06:16,160
[Taichi: Are you gonna date him
just because you feel bad? No.]

1271
01:06:16,160 --> 01:06:17,940
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Yeah.]

1272
01:06:17,940 --> 01:06:20,520
[Taichi: Anyway, like him,]

1273
01:06:20,520 --> 01:06:22,940
[Taichi: it's an opportunity for you too.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Yeah.]

1274
01:06:22,940 --> 01:06:24,380
[Taichi: Do you see it as a chance?]

1275
01:06:24,380 --> 01:06:27,980
[Taichi: Since you liked someone before.]

1276
01:06:27,980 --> 01:06:30,280
[Taichi: Do you want to win him over?]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: No.]

1277
01:06:30,280 --> 01:06:33,350
[Taichi: Are you over him?]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Yes, of course.]

1278
01:06:33,350 --> 01:06:36,300
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Because he clearly rejected me.]

1279
01:06:36,300 --> 01:06:40,690
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
And I know why he won't fall for me.]

1280
01:06:40,690 --> 01:06:45,640
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
He rejected me up to the last date.]

1281
01:06:45,640 --> 01:06:48,340
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
So there's no reason for me to keep at it.]

1282
01:06:48,340 --> 01:06:51,110
[Taichi: Then is there someone you like now?]

1283
01:06:51,110 --> 01:06:52,460
[Taichi: Someone you want to know better.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Me?]

1284
01:06:52,460 --> 01:06:54,800
[Taichi: Yeah.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Yeah, I do.]

1285
01:06:55,890 --> 01:07:01,760
[Lee Hyeok Jin: I'm so confused now.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Me too.]

1286
01:07:01,760 --> 01:07:03,530
[Lee Hyeok Jin: They both took good care of me.]

1287
01:07:03,530 --> 01:07:06,300
[Lee Hyeok Jin:
Han Gyeol was more caring than I thought.]

1288
01:07:06,300 --> 01:07:07,590
[Eum Hyeok Jin: To you?]
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Yeah.]

1289
01:07:07,590 --> 01:07:10,480
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Hyun Jun too.
It's the first time he's done this...]

1290
01:07:10,480 --> 01:07:12,780
[Lee Hyeok Jin:
When I said I couldn't see the tiger...]

1291
01:07:12,780 --> 01:07:14,290
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Did he lift you by your temples?]

1292
01:07:14,290 --> 01:07:17,410
[Lee Hyeok Jin:
He dragged me to the front like this.]

1293
01:07:17,410 --> 01:07:20,840
[Lee Hyeok Jin: So I thought,
could it be a good sign?]

1294
01:07:20,840 --> 01:07:24,270
[Eum Hyeok Jin: You may see it that way,]

1295
01:07:24,270 --> 01:07:28,980
[Eum Hyeok Jin: but from what I know of him,
I think he just did it out of kindness.]

1296
01:07:28,980 --> 01:07:32,780
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Since you said you couldn't see.]
[Taichi: I think so too. If it's Hyun Jun.]

1297
01:07:33,170 --> 01:07:36,060
[Taichi: But right now, it seems like]

1298
01:07:36,060 --> 01:07:42,250
[Taichi: Hyun Jun isn't into any one person.]
[Lee Hyeok Jin: That's why I'm going for it.]

1299
01:07:42,250 --> 01:07:44,720
[Lee Hyeok Jin: I want to give it a go
without pressuring him.]

1300
01:07:44,720 --> 01:07:46,000
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Right.]

1301
01:07:46,000 --> 01:07:48,820
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Everyone's bored, right?]

1302
01:07:48,820 --> 01:07:51,480
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Let's play Never Have I Ever.]

1303
01:07:52,970 --> 01:07:55,180
[Oh Min Seong: Us five?]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Yeah.]

1304
01:07:56,060 --> 01:07:59,920
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Let's play.]
[Oh Min Seong: OK.]

1305
01:07:59,920 --> 01:08:02,240
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Let's play.]

1306
01:08:02,240 --> 01:08:04,680
[Kim Han Gyeol: Suddenly?]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Suddenly! Who will go first?]

1307
01:08:04,680 --> 01:08:05,830
[Oh Min Seong: Let's go anticlockwise.]

1308
01:08:05,830 --> 01:08:08,130
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Me first?]
[Oh Min Seong: Yeah.]

1309
01:08:08,830 --> 01:08:13,120
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Put a finger down]

1310
01:08:13,120 --> 01:08:16,319
[Lee Hyeong Jun: If you're
not interested in anyone in this room now.]

1311
01:08:17,160 --> 01:08:18,680
[Kim Han Gyeol: All five of us here.]

1312
01:08:18,680 --> 01:08:21,250
[Puts a finger down]

1313
01:08:22,649 --> 01:08:23,000
[Lee Hyun Jun: What do you mean?]

1314
01:08:23,000 --> 01:08:23,760
Darn it.

1315
01:08:23,760 --> 01:08:24,750
No...

1316
01:08:26,850 --> 01:08:28,200
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Did you put a finger down?]
[Kim Han Gyeol: Yes.]

1317
01:08:28,200 --> 01:08:30,020
[Lee Hyeong Jun: No one here?]
[Kim Han Gyeol: Yes.]

1318
01:08:30,020 --> 01:08:31,290
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Really?]

1319
01:08:31,590 --> 01:08:33,790
[Oh Min Seong: I'm a bit hurt.]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I'm hurt.]

1320
01:08:33,790 --> 01:08:34,420
[Lee Hyun Jun: So ruthless.]

1321
01:08:34,420 --> 01:08:35,130
Seriously.

1322
01:08:35,270 --> 01:08:37,800
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Not interested in us 4 at all.]
[Oh Min Seong: I'm hurt.]

1323
01:08:38,740 --> 01:08:41,250
[Lee Hyeong Jun:
And 4 of us didn't put a finger down?]

1324
01:08:41,250 --> 01:08:42,160
[Oh Min Seong: Yes.]

1325
01:08:42,160 --> 01:08:44,029
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Really? Wow.]

1326
01:08:47,490 --> 01:08:49,880
[Just as it's getting awkward, a phone rings]

1327
01:08:49,880 --> 01:08:50,990
Do you have to go somewhere?

1328
01:08:50,990 --> 01:08:56,130
[Hyeong Jun got a text?]

1329
01:09:00,660 --> 01:09:04,340
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Who are you giving (the gift) to?]
[Kim Sun Wook: Me?]

1330
01:09:04,340 --> 01:09:05,529
[Kim Sun Wook: I've put it in.]

1331
01:09:05,529 --> 01:09:10,540
[Kim Sun Wook: Who are you giving it to?]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I've changed my mind.]

1332
01:09:11,930 --> 01:09:14,649
[Kim Sun Wook: You've changed your mind?]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Yeah.]

1333
01:09:14,970 --> 01:09:18,160
[Lee Hyeong Jun: About 5 minutes ago.]
[Kim Sun Wook: What do you mean?]

1334
01:09:18,569 --> 01:09:20,540
[A gift full of sincerity for their crush]

1335
01:09:20,779 --> 01:09:28,520
[Who will they convey their true feelings to?]

1336
01:09:35,220 --> 01:09:37,439
[Oh Min Seong: Shoot, it's here again.
The Anonymous Chat.]

1337
01:09:37,439 --> 01:09:40,430
[Oh Min Seong: But it came early in this season.]

1338
01:09:40,430 --> 01:09:42,500
[Taichi: I think I'm at a disadvantage.]

1339
01:09:42,500 --> 01:09:44,439
[Taichi: After all, I'm Japanese.]

1340
01:09:44,660 --> 01:09:47,689
[Kim Sun Wook: I don't think it's us.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Yeah, I agree.]

1341
01:09:48,029 --> 01:09:50,180
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I'm a little nervous.]

1342
01:09:50,180 --> 01:09:52,500
[Lee Hyeong Jun:
I don't know what to talk about.]

1343
01:09:52,500 --> 01:09:54,750
[Park Jae Ha:
I want to know Hyeong Jun's feelings.]

1344
01:09:54,750 --> 01:09:57,660
[Park Jae Ha:
I finally have a chance to ask him.]

1345
01:09:57,890 --> 01:10:00,620
[How will the nerve-racking Anonymous Chat
influence their unpredictable affections?]
